## JSON Serialization Pattern
```dart
// Saving list of models
List<Pet> pets = [...];
String json = jsonEncode(pets.map((p) => p.toJson()).toList());
await prefs.setString(StorageKeys.pets, json);

// Loading list of models
String? json = prefs.getString(StorageKeys.pets);
if (json != null) {
  List<dynamic> decoded = jsonDecode(json);
  List<Pet> pets = decoded.map((item) => Pet.fromJson(item)).toList();
}
```
